{"title":"机器学习-初笔记","uid":"d3ac86dbd4d2ee7d28228084ddf9f593","slug":"笔记/机器学习/初笔记","date":"2025-10-16T08:11:00.000Z","updated":"2025-11-13T08:37:14.822Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/笔记/机器学习/初笔记.json","keywords":null,"cover":"img/post/笔记/机器学习/初笔记/cover.webp","content":"<h1 id=\"一-术语\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#一-术语\"></a> 一. 术语</h1>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">术语</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">权重<br>Weights</td>\n<td>从训练集自动学习的到的参数</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">超参数<br>Hyperparameters</td>\n<td>1. 训练前人为指定的参数<br>2. 例如：网络层数、激活函数、学习率、Epoch等</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">Epoch</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h1 id=\"二-介绍\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#二-介绍\"></a> 二. 介绍</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1-学习的定义\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#1-学习的定义\"></a> 1. 学习的定义</h2>\n<p>机器学习需要任务 Task <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">T</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">T</span></span></span></span>，性能评估 Performance measure <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">P</span></span></span></span> 和 训练样例 Training experience <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>E</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">E</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">E</span></span></span></span>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-如何定义一个学习系统\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#2-如何定义一个学习系统\"></a> 2. 如何定义一个学习系统</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">步骤</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">收集训练样例<br>Collect Training Experience</td>\n<td>例如调查、计算机生成</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">表示样例<br>Representing Experience</td>\n<td>即对样例进行编码，样例 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>E</mi><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>X</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>D</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">E = (X, D)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">E</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">X</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span><br>1. <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">X</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">X</span></span></span></span> 为特征向量(Feature Vector) 由多维的向量表示<br>2. <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">D</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span></span></span></span> 为对应向量(Corresponding Vector)，用来记录特征向量 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">X</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">X</span></span></span></span> 的结果/分类<br>4. 因此模型是一个 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>D</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">X \\to D</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">X</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span></span></span></span> 的映射/函数</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">选择函数</td>\n<td>选择函数 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>W</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>X</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F(W, X)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">W</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">X</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> 来对 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">X</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">X</span></span></span></span> 分类成 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">D</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span></span></span></span><br>1. <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>W</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">W</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">W</span></span></span></span> 表示可以调整的参数/权重(Weights)<br>2. <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>W</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">W</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">W</span></span></span></span> 就是学习算法进行学习的东西</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">学习权重</td>\n<td>选择一个学习算法来调整权重 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>W</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">W</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">W</span></span></span></span> 并预测</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">调整权重</td>\n<td>计算并利用错误指标 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>Error</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\text{Error}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">Error</span></span></span></span></span> 来进行调整权重<br>1. 简单的错误计算 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mtext>Error</mtext><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∣</mi><mi>D</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>W</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>X</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∣</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\text{Error} = |D - F(W, X)|</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">Error</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">∣</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">W</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">X</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mord\">∣</span></span></span></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">使用/测试系统</td>\n<td>1. 一旦学习完成，所有的权重就是确定的了<br>2. 给出任意未知 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">X</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">X</span></span></span></span> 该系统都可以计算出一个答案 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>W</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>X</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F(W, X)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">W</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">X</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>例如在 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>8</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">8 \\times 8</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.72777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">8</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">8</span></span></span></span> 画布识别 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mn>0</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mn>9</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">[0, 9]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">[</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">9</span><span class=\"mclose\">]</span></span></span></span> 数字系统中，<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">X</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">X</span></span></span></span> 表示一个 64-d 的二进制向量用来描述画布的像素情况，而 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">D</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span></span></span></span> 表示 10-d 的二进制向量用来表示是哪个数字。如果为数字 2, 则只有第三维向量为 1，其他为 0 (第一维从 0 开始)。</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-特征空间-feature-space\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#3-特征空间-feature-space\"></a> 3. 特征空间 （Feature Space）</h2>\n<p>特征空间是一个由特征组成的数学空间，数据集中每一个样本都可以表示为该空间的一个点或向量。该过程是 从对象(Objects) 到 特征向量(Feature Vectors, <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">X</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">X</span></span></span></span>) 到 特征空间的点。</p>\n<p>对于 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 个特征的特征空间是一个 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 维的超空间。</p>\n<h2 id=\"4-学习系统种类\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#4-学习系统种类\"></a> 4. 学习系统种类</h2>\n<p>学习系统一般分为 分类(Classification) 和 回归(Regression)</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\"></th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">分类</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">回归</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">预测</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">标签<br>Label</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">回应<br>Response</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">输出</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">离散的值<br>Discrete</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">连续的值<br>Continuous</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">例子</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">预测一个图片是猫还是狗</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">预测明天的股票</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"i-分类学习\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#i-分类学习\"></a> i. 分类学习</h3>\n<p>分类学习一般有 监督学习(Supervised Learning) 和 非监督学习 (Unsupervised Learning)。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\"></th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">监督学习<br>Supervised Learning</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">非监督学习<br>Unsupervised Learning</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">弱监督学习<br>Weakly supervised learning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">数据</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">输入-输出对<br>包含标签的</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">未包含标签的</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">半包含标签的</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">学习</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">将输入映射到输出的函数</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">数据集中元素之间的关系<br>无需帮助即可分类</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">应用</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">图像识别</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">数据聚类<br>Data Clustering</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"5-过拟合与拟合不足\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#5-过拟合与拟合不足\"></a> 5. 过拟合与拟合不足</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\"></th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">过拟合<br>Overfitting</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">拟合不足<br>Underfitting</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">发生情况</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">1. 学习时间过长<br>2. 训练样本无法代表所有可能的情况 (通常)<br>3. 参数调整到与真实目标函数没有因果关系的无信息特征(Uninformative Features)上</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">解决方法</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">1. 增加训练集的大小<br>2. 交叉验证(Cross Validation)</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"6-交叉验证\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#6-交叉验证\"></a> 6. 交叉验证</h2>\n<p>交叉验证(Cross Validation) 是一种减少过拟合的方法。</p>\n<p>交叉验证将收集到的数据分为训练集、验证集、测试集。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">数据集</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">参与训练</th>\n<th>作用</th>\n<th>用途</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">训练集<br>Training Set</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">✔️</td>\n<td>拟合权重参数</td>\n<td>让模型学会如何做任务</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">验证集<br>Validation Set</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">✖️</td>\n<td>评估模型在未见过的数据上的表现</td>\n<td>1. 超参数调节<br>2. 模型比较和选择<br>3. 防止过拟合选择最好的 Epoch</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">测试集<br>Test Set</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">✖️</td>\n<td>完全独立的数据<br>在任何训练过程中不会出现</td>\n<td>1. 模型最终性能报告和评估<br>2. 对模型泛化性做出最终客观评价</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n","feature":false,"text":"关于机器学习大杂烩笔记。...","permalink":"/post/笔记/机器学习/初笔记","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"笔记-机器学习","slug":"笔记-机器学习","count":1,"path":"api/categories/笔记-机器学习.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Machine Learning","slug":"Machine-Learning","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Machine-Learning.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80-%E6%9C%AF%E8%AF%AD\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 一. 术语</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C-%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 二. 介绍</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\"> 1. 学习的定义</span></a></li><li cla